original: Larsson, Gösta Emil, tandläkare, Karlskrona, f. 6/6/07 i Skultuna, Väst-mani. L, av Karl L. o. Agnes HalHn. G. 37 m. Vaja Svensson, Barn: Sten-Lennart f, 42, Leif Arne 45, — Stud:-ex. i Karlskrona 28, Cand. med. dent. i Leipzig 30, tysk tandläkare där 32, sv, dito 35. Praktik i Karlskrona sed, 35, skoltandl. i Nättraby sed. 36.
translated: Larsson, Gösta Emil, dentist, Karlskrona, b. 6/6/07 in Skultuna, Väst-mani. Son of Karl L. and Agnes HalHn. Married in 1937 to Vaja Svensson. Children: Sten-Lennart b. 1942, Leif Arne b. 1945. Passed student examination in Karlskrona in 1928, obtained a dental degree in Leipzig in 1930, worked as a German dentist there in 1932, and as a Swedish dentist in 1935. Practiced in Karlskrona since 1935, and as a school dentist in Nättraby since 1936.
